    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1">Solids In Active or All Mechanisms</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Heading3_atocs_">Visibility toolbar &gt; Show Solids in Active or All Mechanism-Editors</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text"><text styleclass="Notes">NOTE </text>- there is <text styleclass="VariableName" style="color:#ff0000;">not</text> a <text styleclass="T_Menu">Visibility </text><text styleclass="T_Menu" style="color:#ff0000;">menu</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">This command relates to <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-POP-Solids" styleclass="Interface">Solid</link> and <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-POP-Plane" styleclass="Interface">Plane</link> elements.</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">Use this command to toggle between: <text styleclass="VariableName">Show Solids (and Planes) in only the active Mechanism-Editor </text>OR to <text styleclass="VariableName">See Solids (and Planes) in ALL Mechanism-Editors</text>.</para>
